# LeakSanitizer suppressions for gRParse test binaries.
#
# Use with: LSAN_OPTIONS=suppressions=tests/lsan.supp
#
# Poppler's GlobalParams::findSystemFontFile asks fontconfig for a base-14
# substitute the first time a page is rasterized. fontconfig caches its parsed
# XML configuration in process-global state and never frees it, so LSan reports
# it once per process. It is a fixed one-time allocation, not a per-page or
# per-document leak, and it lives entirely in third-party code.
leak:libfontconfig
leak:libexpat
